<p xml:lang="est">Published 10/14/2012 Updated 4/4/2017</p>
<p>An overarching goal for all environmental work is sustainable development. Environmental protection is a broad professional field, covering everything from land management to natural diversity and the management of fish and game.</p>
<p>Every sector has a responsibility to take environmental concerns into account in their own operations. The County Governor must help to ensure that the government’s environmental and land management policies are implemented on both a regional and a local level. Municipalities play a key role in efforts to protect the environment. Municipal guidance and supervision are therefore important tasks for us.</p>
